						<summary>

						<p>A fragment of a slab spread on the platform under the <hi rend="italic">margōsa</hi> tree near the well called Bommanabhāvi.</p>						

						<p>18th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This undated inscription can be assigned to 18th century on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>Incomplete and registers contributions levied on the produce of grain in the village. It also mentions certain Venkaṭādhirāja.</p>						

						</summary>
